{"pageProps":{"industriesData":{"id":"aTqPyhAAACEAvff0","uid":null,"url":"/industries","type":"industries","href":"https://EXTNGO.cdn.prismic.io/api/v2/documents/search?ref=aa6GrxIAACIArDv7&q=%5B%5B%3Ad+%3D+at%28document.id%2C+%22aTqPyhAAACEAvff0%22%29+%5D%5D","tags":[],"first_publication_date":"2025-12-11T09:33:15+0000","last_publication_date":"2026-02-16T18:08:48+0000","slugs":["industries"],"linked_documents":[],"lang":"en-us","alternate_languages":[],"data":{"hero_title":"Supporting the \nindustries that move \nthe world forward.","hero_text":"Across aeronautics, space, automotive, and defense, we support teams designing lighter, stronger, and more efficient structures for the next generation of mobility.","carousel_slides":[{"main_title":"aeronautics","secondary_title":"Aeronautics","description":"Aircraft push the limits of weight, cost, and emissions. Legacy composites hold them back. EXTNGO's steered fiber composites unlock the lightest, strongest structures possible, built faster, and at scale.","image":{"dimensions":{"width":2160,"height":1400},"alt":null,"copyright":null,"url":"https://images.prismic.io/EXTNGO/aZM7XFWLo0XkEjD3_Frame1197134277.jpg?auto=format,compress","id":"aZM7XFWLo0XkEjD3","edit":{"x":0,"y":0,"zoom":1,"background":"transparent"}}},{"main_title":"Defense","secondary_title":"Defense","description":"Factories win wars. Nearly all modern defense already rely on composites to drive performance. EXTNGO's production system can not only give an edge in performance but can rapidly set-up automated production lines anywhere in the world to ensure sovereignty.","image":{"dimensions":{"width":2880,"height":1866},"alt":"Defense","copyright":null,"url":"https://images.prismic.io/EXTNGO/aTqQr3NYClf9oDYe_20.png?auto=format,compress","id":"aTqQr3NYClf9oDYe","edit":{"x":0,"y":0,"zoom":1,"background":"transparent"}}},{"main_title":"Space","secondary_title":"Space","description":"In orbit, every gram counts. EXTNGO makes steered composites ultra-light, defect-free, and scalable. In return, spacecraft gain more efficiency, payload, and mission certainty.","image":{"dimensions":{"width":2880,"height":1866},"alt":"Space","copyright":null,"url":"https://images.prismic.io/EXTNGO/aTqQ7XNYClf9oDYv_07.png?auto=format,compress","id":"aTqQ7XNYClf9oDYv","edit":{"x":0,"y":0,"zoom":1,"background":"transparent"}}},{"main_title":"Automotive","secondary_title":"Automotive","description":"Performance, cost, and design freedom should never be tradeoffs. EXTNGO frees automakers from the constraints of legacy composites to deliver, lighter, safer, more radical structures, affordably and at scale.","image":{"dimensions":{"width":2880,"height":1866},"alt":"automotive","copyright":null,"url":"https://images.prismic.io/EXTNGO/aVvLw3NYClf9oyfm_06.png?auto=format,compress","id":"aVvLw3NYClf9oyfm","edit":{"x":0,"y":0,"zoom":1,"background":"transparent"}}}],"center_heading_text":"Trusted by teams who \ncan’t afford compromise.","trusted_teams_title":"Reliable by design.","trusted_teams_heading":"They choose EXTNGO because we deliver what was previously considered impossible: steered fiber, defect-free composite structures, produced at industrial speed and with certainty.","trusted_teams_description":"We work with engineers operating where performance, reliability, and scale are non-negotiable.","trusted_teams_icons":[{"icon":{"dimensions":{"width":92,"height":54},"alt":" Joby Logo","copyright":null,"url":"https://images.prismic.io/EXTNGO/aTv0XXNYClf9oG03_Vector.png?auto=format,compress","id":"aTv0XXNYClf9oG03","edit":{"x":0,"y":0,"zoom":1,"background":"transparent"}}},{"icon":{"dimensions":{"width":248,"height":27},"alt":"BAE Systems logo","copyright":null,"url":"https://images.prismic.io/EXTNGO/aTv0XHNYClf9oG02_Logotext.png?auto=format,compress","id":"aTv0XHNYClf9oG02","edit":{"x":0,"y":0,"zoom":1,"background":"transparent"}}},{"icon":{"dimensions":{"width":306,"height":40},"alt":"Hyundai logo","copyright":null,"url":"https://images.prismic.io